Package com.itsradiix.discordwebhook.embed.models

Class Field

java.lang.Object
com.itsradiix.discordwebhook.embed.models.Field
public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
The Field class represents a field in an embedded message. Make sure to read the wiki page on our GitHub to understand how to use this effectively. https://github.com/ItsRadiiX/Definity-Webhooks/wiki

    • Field

      public Field​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String value, boolean inline)
      Full Constructor for Creating an Field Object. You can set the inline to whatever you want.

  • Method Details

    • checkIfEmpty

      private java.lang.String checkIfEmpty​(java.lang.String s)
      This method checks whether or not the Field is empty. If so, it will set the default UniCode for a Space, that way Discord API will not return a bad request.
      Parameters:
      s - String to be checked.
      Returns:
      String Returns String with UniCode for a Space Set.
